8年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160725/914826/ |title=爆張顯耀案內幕　金溥聰：助理與台商合作洩密 |accessdate=2020-09-20 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112090251/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160725/914826/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
